    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/00a91f0d9d0046ed82ce4edaa74cdca9.poster.avif?t=1765584616\" width=640 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/00a91f0d9d0046ed82ce4edaa74cdca9.webm?t=1765584616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/00a91f0d9d0046ed82ce4edaa74cdca9.mp4?t=1765584616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/e0868402bce5b23a805edd50a847a058.poster.avif?t=1765584616\" width=558 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/e0868402bce5b23a805edd50a847a058.webm?t=1765584616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/e0868402bce5b23a805edd50a847a058.mp4?t=1765584616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Return to the world of <i>Psychopomp</i>.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden under every building, under every place, is a catacomb.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Labyrinths stretching down into the bowels and guts of the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everyone has known about them. Everyone has lied to you about them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Descend into the depths, discover what awaits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/dc4f09b5f4f4ca8269589c67f46456de.poster.avif?t=1765584616\" width=526 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/dc4f09b5f4f4ca8269589c67f46456de.webm?t=1765584616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/dc4f09b5f4f4ca8269589c67f46456de.mp4?t=1765584616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The hit horror dungeon crawler is BACK!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now with all sorts of new horrifying cool stuff to see!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a classic 3D dungeon crawler world, discover secrets below, and find the truth that awaits. Bizarre, unique creatures are at every turn, and even weirder things lie below!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/6ef12a41f3378ef5e2809d7875e562ec.poster.avif?t=1765584616\" width=558 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/6ef12a41f3378ef5e2809d7875e562ec.webm?t=1765584616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/6ef12a41f3378ef5e2809d7875e562ec.mp4?t=1765584616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/54ba06ebb1f5376d6412e29f977583bc.poster.avif?t=1765584616\" width=138 height=104 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/54ba06ebb1f5376d6412e29f977583bc.webm?t=1765584616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/54ba06ebb1f5376d6412e29f977583bc.mp4?t=1765584616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/439359cc89d322053667f49a4fc0e09b.poster.avif?t=1765584616\" width=138 height=104 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/439359cc89d322053667f49a4fc0e09b.webm?t=1765584616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/439359cc89d322053667f49a4fc0e09b.mp4?t=1765584616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/54ba06ebb1f5376d6412e29f977583bc.poster.avif?t=1765584616\" width=138 height=104 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/54ba06ebb1f5376d6412e29f977583bc.webm?t=1765584616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/54ba06ebb1f5376d6412e29f977583bc.mp4?t=1765584616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/439359cc89d322053667f49a4fc0e09b.poster.avif?t=1765584616\" width=138 height=104 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/439359cc89d322053667f49a4fc0e09b.webm?t=1765584616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/439359cc89d322053667f49a4fc0e09b.mp4?t=1765584616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Psychopomp GOLD features:</strong></i></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All new levels - Delve deeper than ever before!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remastered Levels - See the horrors in a brand new light!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New Modes and Secrets - Discover what is to be seen. Find what has been hidden from you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New Endings!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improved old Endings!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mod and Custom Level Support - The Catacombs will Never End!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New Prerendered Cutscenes - Get a Cinematic Feel.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Third Person Mode - A new view on life!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter the catacombs, and immerse yourself in a world that only grows darker the deeper you get. This meat is what the world is made of.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep your wits about you, watch your back, and survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>Warning:</i> Psychopomp is designed around the Vulkan renderer, which may not work on older PCs. The game can run on OpenGL, but it is not recommended.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/6542bd08df4b84aee6e0f573043407c5.poster.avif?t=1765584616\" width=186 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/6542bd08df4b84aee6e0f573043407c5.webm?t=1765584616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/6542bd08df4b84aee6e0f573043407c5.poster.avif?t=1765584616\" width=186 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/6542bd08df4b84aee6e0f573043407c5.webm?t=1765584616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/6542bd08df4b84aee6e0f573043407c5.poster.avif?t=1765584616\" width=186 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243190/extras/6542bd08df4b84aee6e0f573043407c5.webm?t=1765584616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
